

 How 2-way data-binding happening NG ?
 
 
 NG - LifeCycle
 ------------------
 
  compilation-phase/parsing
  
  on every DOM element which are having 'directives'/'expressions'
  will register 'watch' expressions ( listeners )
 
 
  'watch' expression are executed by 'digest-loop'
  
  
  -----------------------
  
  we can also register 'custom watch expressions'
  
